Then $OD^2 = 1,$ and $OA^2 = 9,$ so by the Pythagorean Theorem on right triangle $OAD,$
\[AD^2 = OA^2 - OD^2 = 8.\]Then $AD = 2 \sqrt{2},$ so the area of the circle is $\pi AD^2 = \boxed{16 \pi}.$

